## Collection of Routine Information

The Belcoda application, this website, and other Belcoda products track basic information about their visitors and users.  
This information includes, but is not limited to, IP addresses, browser details, timestamps, and referring pages.  
None of this information can personally identify specific visitors or users.  
The information is tracked for routine administration and maintenance purposes.

## Collection of Personal Information

As part of the necessary operations of Belcoda products, this website, and the Belcoda application, certain personal information is collected.  This information includes, but is not limited to, email addresses, phone numbers, and names.  This information is used to create user accounts, send notifications, and provide customer support.  This information is stored securely and is not shared with third parties.

Self-hosted instances of the Belcoda application do **not** transmit personal information to Belcoda LLC.  The personal information collected via self-hosted instances of the Belcoda application is stored on the instance manager's infrastructure and is not accessible by Belcoda LLC. Depending on its configuration settings, a self-hosted Belcoda instance may transmit routine information to Belcoda LLC.  This information includes, but is not limited to, IP addresses, browser details, timestamps, and referring pages.  None of this information can personally identify specific visitors or users.  The information is tracked for routine administration and maintenance purposes.

